# Quality gates

Run all checks before opening a PR. CI enforces the same commands.
{% if python != 'none' %}
## Commands
{% if python == 'root' %}
```bash
uv run poe check         # full CI suite: format-check + lint + typecheck + test with coverage

uv run poe fix           # auto-fix: format + lint --fix (safe to run anytime)
uv run poe test          # run tests only (no coverage, faster)
uv run poe test_cov      # run tests with coverage report
uv run poe lint          # ruff check only
uv run poe typecheck     # pyright only
```
{% else %}
