## Pre-commit hooks
{% if hooks == 'none' %}
No pre-commit hooks are configured for this project.
{% else %}
Pre-commit hooks run automatically on `git commit`.

```bash
# Install hooks after cloning
pre-commit install

# Run manually against all files
pre-commit run --all-files
```

